# Local

bundle install
rake db:migrate 

# Demo

## Create

heroku create ryancontact
git push heroku master
heroku rake db:migrate

## Scale

heroku ps
heroku dynos +10
heroku ps
heroku dynos 1

## Extend and Introspect

heroku addons:add memcache:5mb 

heroku addons:add pgbackups:basic
heroku pgbackups:capture
heroku pgbackups **

heroku logs

## Redeploy

touch DEMO
git push heroku master

